Subject: Upgrade NEA
Description: Customer would like to upgrade NEA from 11.5 to 11.6
What_We_Know__c: NEA was upgraded to version 11.6.0.115 successfully, however AIC upgrade is not working. AIC installs and the service starts, but the port never binds and there are no logs indicating any issues.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
Customer requested upgrade of AIC and NEA to latest version.


Resolution
Upgrade completed successfully.
